Search Buttons Bar v1.1 (released 2016-06-06)
- Add basic options.
- Add option to select search buttons to show.
- Add icon for the addon.
- Fix issues with latest Firefox.
- Fix styling issue of search bar text field with Windows High Contrast theme.
- Fix search bar resizing splitters visibility.
- Fix open in new tab option.
- Fix removing of default search engines.
